title: Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1985-03-28
lineage: master cassette > tcd5m (original recorder +dolby) > minime (24/96) > sd744t > audacity > xact (flac24)
description:
Set 1

Truckin'-> Smokestack Lightning*-> High Time, El Paso, Peggy-O, Cassidy, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Looks Like Rain-> Drums-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> The Other One-> Black Peter-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Day Job

reviews.review_text: oh so sweet... sound is clear enough. band is on, jerry's voice... is jerry's voice... :)...

Sweet and steady 1st set followed by a 2nd that's brilliant but a lot better up to Space than it is after.
4.4 1st
4.3 2nd
encore nothing special.
